    "Preparing dataThis is the initial step for model development.",
    "First step in preporcessing is normalization and detrending to convert the input data into a stationary time series.",
    "Next, we calculate the extreme value indicator using a Gaussian Mixture Model (GMM).",
    "GMM model uses a weighted average of 3 components for calculating extreme values indicator sequence for all time series sequences.",
    "This indicator is then concatenated with the input time series data to provide a comprehensive dataset."
